Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.97,0:01:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們三個人成立了學園偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.41,0:01:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想用活動來舉行首次演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.46,0:01:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穗乃果…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.48,0:01:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不知道做不做得成呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.27,0:01:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  當然要做的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.98,0:01:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.35,0:01:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在還沒有登台的水準…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.24,0:01:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行嗎  就憑你們現在這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.14,0:01:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒  沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.58,0:01:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新生歡迎會可不是扮家家酒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.48,0:01:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們三人只是要使用講堂的許可而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.31,0:01:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是社團
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.84,0:01:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生會應該沒有權力對內容說三道四
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.94,0:01:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.03,0:01:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.55,0:01:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你要幫她們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.77,0:01:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管弄多少次都告訴我要這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.54,0:01:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔羅牌！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.64,0:02:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔羅牌是這樣告訴我的！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.63,0:03:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是跟你說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別聲張學園偶像  先把場地什麼的確保好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.32,0:03:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是麵包嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家是和式點心店啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我很少吃麵包的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.54,0:03:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在午飯前吃…會胖的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.79,0:03:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們看了公告板了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要開始做學園偶像了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒想到海未也會參與啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在公告板上貼了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.43,0:04:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  演唱會的通知
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下不到一個月了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻什麼也沒有做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的想法太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是小鳥說可以這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這種感覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看  我設計了下演出服裝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.91,0:04:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的曲線很難
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先試著做一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.59,0:04:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海未你覺得怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可愛吧  很可愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡細長的東西是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腿喲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要光著腿穿這麼短的裙子嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:05:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.86,0:05:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對沒事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.03,0:05:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海未的腿沒那麼胖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有資格說別人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  減肥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你們兩個都沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他還有很多要決定的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.80,0:05:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簽名  走在路上時候的變裝方法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些根本不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,組合的名字還沒決定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到什麼好名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們三人要有什麼特徵就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.12,0:05:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三人的性格也各不相同
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.95,0:05:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就乾脆用三個人的名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.21,0:05:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穗乃果  海未  小鳥  請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們叫穗乃果  海未  小鳥！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著像相聲演員
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.17,0:06:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.97,0:06:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海未是海  小鳥是空
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.30,0:06:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穗乃果是陸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就叫海陸空！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守護吧！市民的和平！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不像是偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.89,0:06:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那…  對了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.95,0:06:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36\fad(200,0)}（然後…徵集組合名字！）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部交給別人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.37,0:06:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話大家也能提起點興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.71,0:06:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  接下來是歌曲和舞蹈的練習
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡會妨礙到別人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也全部被佔滿了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:06:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎖住了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空教室不能用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空教室？  你們要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園偶像的練習
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們？偶像？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  被嘲笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.66,0:07:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似只剩這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有遮陽的地方  下雨時就沒法用了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.17,0:07:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要求也不能高呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在這裡不用太在意音量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  努力加油練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先從歌聲的練習開始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,練什麼歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:07:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:07:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花陽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.87,0:08:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好  穗乃果呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在樓上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  要吃團子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  我必須要減肥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.74,0:08:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,練習辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.91,0:08:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃團子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上給你倒茶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…減肥呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.55,0:08:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來沒有要下定決心努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.63,0:08:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那歌曲方面怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.14,0:09:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  高一裡有個唱得非常好的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.68,0:09:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋼琴也彈得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定還會作曲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我決定明天去問一下她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.31,0:09:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能幫我們作曲的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作詞方面就差不多解決了  剛才我們得出了結論
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.49,0:09:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹  幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.37,0:09:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海未你啊  初中的時候寫過詩什麼的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.88,0:09:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有叫我們讀過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.47,0:09:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手  我要回家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海未…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  為什麼為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.73,0:09:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初中那時的事現在都害羞得不敢去回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.78,0:09:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有句話說  偶像要拋棄羞恥嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:09:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:10:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我光製作服裝就很吃力了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是還有穗乃果嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提出來的可是你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.66,0:10:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  其實我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.08,0:10:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包子  和松鼠團子  都吃膩了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得行不通嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.84,0:10:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那確實…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.30,0:10:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了  只有海未你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.84,0:10:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也會幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能寫多少是多少
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海未  拜託了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你太狡猾了  小鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.49,0:10:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.82,0:10:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你會這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  演唱會之前的練習表由我負責
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.79,0:10:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,練習表？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.38,0:10:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們看起來很開心地在歌唱  但身體一直在動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這樣呼吸卻很流暢  而且保持著笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.46,0:10:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這需要大量的體力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穗乃果  能做一下伏地挺身嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.35,0:11:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.56,0:11:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣笑一個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持這樣做伏地挺身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.69,0:11:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.94,0:11:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在弓道部鍛鍊過了先不談
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穗乃果和小鳥必須要有保持笑容唱歌的體力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎  偶像也挺夠嗆的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太難過了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.47,0:11:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腿已經動不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來每天早上和傍晚在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和舞蹈唱歌分開
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我進行體力訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一天要兩次？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.02,0:11:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然要搞就要搞個像樣的演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.86,0:11:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不那樣的話  是吸引不了學生的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.91,0:12:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那就再來一組
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.16,0:12:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.28,0:12:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副會長？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.87,0:12:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那衣服是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.42,0:12:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裡幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神社是集中了許多祈願的靈性的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.63,0:12:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們三個  既然在用這裡的階梯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.09,0:12:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就順便參拜一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.72,0:12:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望第一次演唱會可以順利舉行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以順利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那三個人  看來是認真的呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.75,0:12:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:13:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年級的各位同學  你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是學校偶像  高坂穗乃果
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  好像完全沒聽說過我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.64,0:13:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.93,0:13:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  穗乃果說的唱歌很好的女孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你  能來一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.15,0:13:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了  我想請你來作曲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是因為你只會唱歌  不會作曲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.49,0:13:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能不會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是不想做而已  那種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.29,0:13:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是為了讓學校吸引更多的學生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.63,0:13:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的歌一定能吸引學生的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.05,0:13:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕  什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟海未一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.68,0:13:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是正常的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得海未寫了那麼好的歌詞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:14:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  如果作曲完成了  就要大家一起唱的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話是這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.36,0:14:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生會長？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.28,0:14:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能來一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  把a和b作為實數的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.12,0:14:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須表示為a+bi的形式我們稱為複數
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說3i…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反效果嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在從來沒有學校偶像的這個學校
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果試著去做然後失敗了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.21,0:14:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家會怎麼想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.34,0:14:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不希望這個學校消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.35,0:14:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為這是真心的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.18,0:14:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不希望你們想得太簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.52,0:14:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能想得太簡單了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.73,0:14:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你終於發現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我也不是隨便玩玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.07,0:14:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海未的訓練表我都有完成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此弄得我渾身酸痛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:14:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我也知道你確實很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.12,0:15:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但學生會長說的話  我們必須正面去接受
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.92,0:15:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  連一個月都不到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要開演唱會的話  至少也要決定好唱什麼歌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在已經沒時間再找作曲者了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.43,0:15:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得只能唱其他的學校偶像的歌曲了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.02,0:15:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,練習怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演唱會  如果有什麼幫得上忙的就說哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.95,0:15:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如照明啊  維持客人的秩序之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.95,0:15:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多要做的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.12,0:15:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.08,0:15:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因為穗乃果你們為了學校在努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班上的同學們也想要為你們打氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.63,0:15:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.38,0:15:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.31,0:15:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.52,0:16:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一張
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.61,0:16:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,u's？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想  應該是繆斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\pos(750,653)}μ's
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.95,0:16:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  肥皂？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.95,0:16:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}（日本一家肥皂廠的名字也叫繆斯）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.49,0:16:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想應該用的是神話中登場的女神的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得不錯  我很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繆斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  從今天開始我們就是繆斯了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.55,0:16:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說她們一直在房頂上練習呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.81,0:16:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到我們學校裡也有人搞學校偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.77,0:16:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花陽  回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.07,0:16:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.32,0:16:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  那孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.16,0:16:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說西木野同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:16:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱歌很好的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.70,0:17:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯沒錯  原來她叫西木野同學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.66,0:17:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  西木野真姬同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找她有事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子她已經回去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.05,0:17:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她應該在音樂室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.88,0:17:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音樂室？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.17,0:17:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子一般不跟大家說話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一到休息時間就去圖書館
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一放學就去音樂室
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.47,0:17:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.27,0:17:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們倆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.48,0:17:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加  加油哦  偶像…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.07,0:17:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我會的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找我有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是想再拜託你一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真纏人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.88,0:17:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  海未一直這麼說我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從來不聽那種音樂的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.59,0:18:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一般都是聽古典和爵士樂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.27,0:18:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.39,0:18:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為流行樂太低級了  感覺很輕薄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種只是隨便玩玩的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是這麼認為的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺像節日一樣  啪的熱鬧起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.78,0:18:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能快樂地唱就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.87,0:18:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  其實還挺辛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.91,0:18:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  你會伏地挺身嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.33,0:18:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.29,0:18:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當  當然會了  那種小事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1  2  3  這樣就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  好厲害  比我做得還多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.80,0:18:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了  別看我這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  就這樣笑一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.56,0:18:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.14,0:18:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就試試
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:19:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  當偶像很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.41,0:19:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.58,0:19:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿著  這是歌詞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試著讀一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是讀一下沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我會來問的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.09,0:19:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時如果你還是說不行的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會乾脆地放棄的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.92,0:19:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得我的回答是不會變的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話  就讓我再聽你唱歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜歡西木野同學的歌聲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.35,0:19:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽了那首歌和鋼琴彈奏太感動了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.81,0:19:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就想要請你幫我作曲了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.95,0:19:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們每天早上和傍晚都在階梯那裡練習
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不介意的話  就來玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜歡西木野同學的歌聲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.63,0:19:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.84,0:19:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經動不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.17,0:20:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  還有兩個來回呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.38,0:20:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說你們要放棄了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.22,0:20:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  海未個惡代官
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.14,0:20:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是鬼教官吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.40,0:20:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.61,0:20:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你  你幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.98,0:20:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來還在發育呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.82,0:20:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只要不放棄希望就可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.53,0:20:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有變大的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.70,0:20:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指的什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.50,0:20:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不好意思的話  也可以偷偷去做哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.13,0:20:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我問你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.17,0:20:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.30,0:20:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.43,0:20:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是姐姐的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.23,0:20:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有寫收信人的名字哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只寫了繆斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.53,0:21:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要放咯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.09,0:21:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這歌聲…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  變成歌曲了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.85,0:21:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.47,0:21:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有排名了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.95,0:21:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  開始練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.95,0:21:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
